    Scope and Contents
SANGAMON ORDNANCE PLANT PROJECT 
Lyon, Illiopolis resident, recalls the Sangamon Ordnance Plant; employment as a guard; retrieval of land; waste dumping; female and minority employees; housing and transportation; local reaction; water and sewer systems; igloos and the burning grounds; security and working for the Director of Safety. Also recalls farming in the 1940's. 1 tape, 45 mins., 19 pp. 
Interview by B. David McCarthy, 1989 
